My sweet Brix, I can’t believe you’re 9. Every year gets harder, I’m not ready for you to grow up. I will always think of you as my baby. You are kind, generous, beautiful and have the most loving heart. You are the biggest blessing to our family and make us so dang proud in all you do. I pray you cherish these years and soak in all the childhood bliss. Happy birthday beauty🤍 we love you Brixtyn Rose!
Some film shots in honor of it being Carina + Ryan’s wedding weekend. Can’t wait to capture these two & celebrate their love.

Happy 30th birthday to my love. To think I’ve been crushing on this guy for half his life is crazy. The memories we’ve made and family we’ve created together is something I will always be grateful for. I will never forget the day we first met, you have been my person ever since. Loving you is easy. You make life fun and work so hard for our family. You are the best girl dad, support system, listening ear, positive & always looking on the bright side. You make everyday better. I’m the lucky one to have witnessed you grow from the little 15 year old to the amazing man you are today. Cheers to this next chapter🤍
